Class Description
Client

DataSet

Base class of a data set.
DataSetInfo
A short summary of a data set.
FileNameCheck
The result of a file name check, for example, for user IDs and data set IDs.
LogLevel
Server log level.
Notification
A notification sent from the server to the clients.
Payload

PayloadResponseMessageGetServerStatus

The configuration of a server.
ServerException
